{"tid":1358171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727出師有名] 齊防具  和理非聲討黑社會  勇武保衛婦孺!!!","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:34:20.000Z","uid":105976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c04f1117f24872e90c02bfa7cb64dddffb3c853","tid":1358171,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:13:47.000Z","msg":"果日<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非聲討黑社會   定勇武保衛婦孺 </span></strong>都要人 一齊入元朗!!!<br />\n和理非都要齊裝備 好撚重要<br />\n班黑社會欺善怕惡  冇裝備就一定打你先<br />\n<br />\n放心警黑一家 一定會幫手打<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以豬嘴+泳鏡+頭盔+護具一定要齊</strong></span><br />\n豬嘴:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357161/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357161/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">泳鏡</span></strong>買岩你SIZE   選隻岩你面型冇gap<br />\n點都有gap就用熱融膠槍 (文具店/五金鋪 50~100蚊)<br />\n補一下d邊位 唔好嫌麻煩  10分鐘補d膠保你成世<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>頭盔</strong></span>就地盤盔or d記 100~300蚊都有  單車盔 又係要岩size<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n護具: (呢樣比較少人有 但對膝條果d好有用) 護膝 護肘  護手其實最好買全覆蓋式<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.mediadecathlon.com/p1562486/k$aaf9d3fac0676fb93b26c7f404e41fa7/sq/.webp?f=1000x1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.mediadecathlon.com%2Fp1562486%2Fk%24aaf9d3fac0676fb93b26c7f404e41fa7%2Fsq%2F.webp%3Ff%3D1000x1000&h=2be98554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nd記又有守龍手套 ($100) , 拳擊手套又係$100  <br />\n再唔係自已去搵金屬防割手套/戰術手套~ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再勁D買電單車裝甲外套<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-Armor-Protective-Motocross-Protection/dp/B07MW28WJH/ref=sr_1_4?keywords=Armor+jacket&amp;qid=1563930719&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMotorcycle-Armor-Protective-Motocross-Protection%2Fdp%2FB07MW28WJH%2Fref%3Dsr_1_4%3Fkeywords%3DArmor%2Bjacket%26qid%3D1563930719%26s%3Dgateway%26sr%3D8-4&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1R6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=7628d7b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Motorcycle-Armor-Protective-Motocross-Protection/dp/B07MW28WJH/ref=sr_1_4?keywords=Armor+jacket&amp;qid=1563930719&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51-Dkah9E2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51-Dkah9E2L.jpg&h=4a9af92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外套黎 平時可以除左佢<br />\n50USD 唔算貴<br />\n<br />\n仲有褲"},{"pid":"6de7ffe0e2ad58b7d56c35bc75a994efa135e3f4","tid":1358171,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"電單車護甲<br />\n自已GOOGLE下邊度有得買~<br />\n<br />\n我見hk有鋪  amazon 淘寶 都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb29c188ff463d4066316489adbe9de1e4f3286","tid":1358171,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1aaafc43d98f773a803970ae0ae4e92c0b1a3f9","tid":1358171,"uid":217844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:27:16.000Z","msg":"買Gear冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但記住個日一定係和理非 到真係冇辦法先要保護自己/身邊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd97be891e9b41672cffe7d2b892d473b7a2f1f3","tid":1358171,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cada0746fbad4a03271a10ecd092607249d7c40","tid":1358171,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"